## Componentes Responsáveis

| Comunicação | Componente | Protocolo |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend ↔ API Core | Frontend Web (Angular) / API REST | HTTPS/REST |
| Wearables ↔ API Core | Dispositivos IoT | HTTPS / MQTT |
| API Core ↔ Fila | MessageQueue | AMQP / RabbitMQ |
| Fila ↔ API IA Externa | AI Adapter | HTTPS/REST |
| Fila ↔ HIS | HIS Integration Module | HL7 / FHIR |
| Fila ↔ Notificações | Notification Service | SMTP / SMS Gateway |

